{"tid":1936933,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［正向積極］入黎比啲意見龍門冰室！","createTime":"2020-03-21T14:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T18:50:04.000Z","uid":16086,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6ccb007385e65b5f715617407eea0b966722ee","tid":1936933,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"首先，之前手足比意見龍門老細，老細有換餐牌有改善，老細好野！支持老細！<br />\n<br />\n我本身食野唔係好叻，但係有問題好嚴重，想同老細講下，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷氣風超大</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食物上到枱，唔夠5mins就吹凍曬，煮得再好都變難食呀<br />\n希望老細搞搞佢<br />\n<br />\n真心，黃店真係唔係大曬，好食真係緊要<br />\n所以大家想黃店好，比意見真係冇問題<br />\n前提係想黃店好，想壯大黃圈<br />\n但係大家同路人，語氣真係好少少，唔該<br />\n唔好忘記老細出錢出力<br />\n唔好比分化五毛帶到風向，唔該"},{"pid":"7064779bdb30f0884666e9f6e882b0cf4c680bcb","tid":1936933,"uid":317376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"黑椒炸帶好撚正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c37e068dd73a6b8fbb4b66f8271a710c38901a","tid":1936933,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7064779bdb30f0884666e9f6e882b0cf4c680bcb","tid":1936933,"uid":317376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"黑椒炸帶好撚正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"新餐牌有咩好食推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2c5b91df795a493cd20cde69ae7509acb9f06d","tid":1936933,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"龍門凍到北極咁都大把信徒去食啦<br />\n使你條柒頭幫人諗計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9750e9d0402568e420975f7be9e305a0cf11de","tid":1936933,"uid":2267,